reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars excellent and adjustable
reviews.reviewText: This organizer shelf is a BOMB because it’s adjustable, and you can use it turned like a 3-tier white corner shelf or straighten it out and use it as a regular tiered shelf. I was surprised by its versatile design and the way I could choose to add space through its arrangement or let it be. It’s made out of bamboo, which is a lot better than cheap MDF, especially in humid environments like ours (Caribbean) It looks really pretty and holds up a lot of jars and bottles.The entire set-up came with easy-to-follow installation directions, making it possible to arrange it in minutes. I like the hooks added to the side that improved the storage options considerably. And for so many functions, it’s surprisingly cost-effective.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This is very esthetically pleasing for my bathroom counter and helps keep my skin and body products on display and organized and I have a lot! Lol. The only gripe I have is that it stains easily and I don’t like that, I wear make up and sometimes when I am washing my face off and go to grab a cleanser, my makeup could get on it. And when I clean it up it won’t always come off easily. If it keeps staining I will probably use contact paper or something similar to decorate it because it is very durable and sturdy and as I said, looks good on the bathroom counter. And it was VERY easy to assemble

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars From mess to clean
reviews.reviewText: The kitchen countertop organizer has been a transformative addition to my culinary space, turning chaos into order with style and efficiency. This sleek and well-designed organizer has proven to be the perfect solution for decluttering my kitchen while maintaining an aesthetic appeal.Its ingenious layout and multiple compartments provide designated spaces for various kitchen essentials, from cutting boards and utensils to spices and condiments. The thoughtful design not only maximizes storage but also ensures quick and easy access to frequently used items, streamlining my cooking process.What sets this organizer apart is its ability to blend seamlessly with my kitchen decor. The neutral tones and modern design complement the existing style without overpowering the space. It's a functional piece that not only brings order but enhances the overall visual appeal of the kitchen.Constructed with durable materials, the countertop organizer exudes quality and longevity. The sturdiness ensures that it can withstand the demands of a busy kitchen while maintaining its organized charm.In summary, the kitchen countertop organizer has been a game-changer, offering a stylish and practical solution to kitchen clutter. It's a must-have for anyone looking to achieve an organized, efficient, and aesthetically pleasing culinary workspace.
